f="https://www.nme.com/news/music/aerosmith-frontman-steven-tylers-sexual-assault-lawsuit-dismissed-3591423">针对泰勒提起的性侵犯诉讼于二月份被驳回</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/aerosmith-make-heartbreaking-decision-to-retire-from-touring-due-to-steven-tylers-vocal-cord-injury-3780616">史密斯飞船因史蒂文·泰勒的声带受伤而做出退出巡演的“令人心碎”的决定</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
